column5: Welcome to The Beach House Bungalow! While the ocean isn't included, most amazingly you can still catch a wave just 7 miles away at NLAND surf park or play beach-less volleyball in the front yard. This Beach themed home is a delight. Just listed on airbnb and super close to Austin, Texas. Dive in!
column8: *Kick your feet back at the Beach House Bungalow!*
